277
00:15:16,954 --> 00:15:17,974
at the beginning of the funnel,

278
00:15:19,095 --> 00:15:21,775
or you can lose fewer users at the end of the funnel.

279
00:15:23,275 --> 00:15:25,976
And looking at this growth in this particular time,

280
00:15:27,336 --> 00:15:29,417
we realized that it was new users

281
00:15:30,097 --> 00:15:31,658
at the beginning of the funnel that was changing.

282
00:15:32,138 --> 00:15:34,460
The retention metrics didn't particularly move.

283
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,901
So okay, that sounds good.

284
00:15:36,941 --> 00:15:39,742
