287
00:15:44,205 --> 00:15:47,026
So this is a graph of overall traffic.

288
00:15:47,967 --> 00:15:51,148
But we're seeing a change in new user acquisition.

289
00:15:51,829 --> 00:15:52,989
Now new user acquisition,

290
