00:19:51,123 --> 00:19:52,564
there's a natural question, which is,

364
00:19:54,105 --> 00:19:55,886
why would there be such a sudden uptick?

365
00:19:56,786 --> 00:19:59,248
Why wouldn't it just be slowly,

366
00:19:59,288 --> 00:20:01,169
there's one thing and then another thing,

