00:29:01,726 --> 00:29:03,707
So first, Roblox is a privately held company.

544
00:29:04,988 --> 00:29:09,851
And so we don't have to worry about external pressures,

545
00:29:09,871 --> 00:29:11,151
which are tough, I'm glad.

546
00:29:13,112 --> 00:29:16,534
At the time when we were going through this phase,

547
00:29:18,649 --> 00:29:20,390
I think a lot of it came down to our culture.

548
00:29:21,330 --> 00:29:25,351
And there were challenges, but what we did was

