00:29:49,329 --> 00:29:51,232
I better hire a thousand people tomorrow

558
00:29:52,033 --> 00:29:53,515
because we're this other company now.

559
00:29:54,497 --> 00:29:55,258
And we didn't do that.

560
00:29:55,638 --> 00:29:57,381
So that seemed to work for us.

